---
layout: layouts/coming-soon.njk
title: Proximamente
description: Stela é o novo modelo de mobilidade sostible de Santiago de Compostela. Proximamente.
permalink: /coming-soon/
eleventyExcludeFromCollections: true
---

<main class="coming-soon">
  <div class="coming-soon__media" aria-hidden="true">
    <img
      class="coming-soon__image"
      src="{{ '/assets/images/autobus/01.jpg' | url }}"
      alt=""
      width="1600"
      height="900"
      decoding="async"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
  </div>

  <div class="coming-soon__veil" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <div class="coming-soon__frame">
    <p class="coming-soon__brand">
      <span class="coming-soon__mark">STELA</span>
      <span class="coming-soon__lockup">
        <span class="coming-soon__lockup-line">Mobilidade</span>
        <span class="coming-soon__lockup-line">Compostela</span>
      </span>
    </p>

    <h1 class="coming-soon__title">Proximamente</h1>

    <p class="coming-soon__lede">
      O novo modelo de mobilidade sostible de Santiago de Compostela.
    </p>
  </div>

  <footer class="coming-soon__footer">
    <a
      class="coming-soon__concello"
      href="{{ site.footer.concello.url }}"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
    >
      <img
        class="coming-soon__concello-image"
        src="{{ '/assets/images/logo-concello-santiago.svg' | url }}"
        alt="{{ site.footer.concello.name }}"
        width="79"
        height="104"
        decoding="async"
      />
    </a>
  </footer>
</main>
